# %% [code]
"""
VRPTW RL v11 -- patched

Bug fixes over the raw v11 draft:
  [FIX-1] OperatorController.act(): log-prior replaced with linear prior.
           np.log(1e-8)=-18.4 was permanently blacklisting operators.
  [FIX-2] HybridFixed / HybridRule: zeroed op_ctrl Q-weights before solve so
           op selection is pure-bandit (fair non-RL baseline, matches v10 intent).
  [FIX-3] Triple-redundant operator signal removed: dw/rw ALNS marginals and
           biased_dw/biased_rw are gone; op_ctrl receives only mode_bandit as prior.
  [FIX-4] op_warmup 256->128, op_target_freq 120->50, op_eps_decay 0.9996->0.9990
           so Q-network is meaningful before early-stop on RC2.
  [FIX-5] Segment reward cost branch: 0.35/0.15 -> 2.5/1.0 (before scale factor)
           so the controller keeps learning after NV locks at BKS.
  [FIX-6] Mode bandits warm-started from MODES destroy/repair biases so domain
           knowledge is preserved without passing biased_dw/rw each iteration.
  [FIX-7] clone_weights / load_weights include per-mode bandit alpha/beta for
           full transfer (Q-net + bandit priors).
  [FIX-8] ThompsonBandit.select() simplified -- prior baked into alpha/beta init.
  [FIX-9] Removed _prior() and _sample_prior() dead-code from OperatorController.
  [FIX-10] Typo 'a\"\"\"' at top of original file fixed.
"""

